{"title":"(Project) 重構以及進階表單驗證","uid":"e5a7a322c9254e18eb9e9fb26face758","slug":"重構以及進階表單驗證","date":"2021-01-20T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.159Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/重構以及進階表單驗證.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>延續上一份<a href=\"https://michael0520.github.io/2021/01/20/%E8%A1%A8%E5%96%AE%E9%A9%97%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C/\">表單驗證筆記</a></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>重構是為了讓程式碼更加簡潔、可動性更高</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的-if-判斷式\"><a href=\"#先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的-if-判斷式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的 if 判斷式\"></a>先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的 if 判斷式</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">if(email.value&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;&#39;)&#123;\n    showError(email,&#39;Email is required&#39;)\n  &#125;else&#123;\n    showSuccess(email);\n  &#125;\n  if(password.value&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;&#39;)&#123;\n    showError(password,&#39;Password is required&#39;)\n  &#125;else&#123;\n    showSuccess(password);\n  &#125;\n  if(confirmPassword.value&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;&#39;)&#123;\n    showError(confirmPassword,&#39;ConfirmPassword is required&#39;)\n  &#125;else&#123;\n    showSuccess(confirmPassword);\n  &#125;</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"更改為-function-將參數用陣列包裹著\"><a href=\"#更改為-function-將參數用陣列包裹著\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更改為 function 將參數用陣列包裹著\"></a>更改為 function 將參數用陣列包裹著</h3><ul>\n<li>建立新的 function 來執行</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; Check require\nconst checkRequired &#x3D; (inputArr&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    inputArr.forEach(input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    console.log(input.value)\n    &#125;)\n&#125;)\n\ncheckRequired([username,email,password,confirmPassword])</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>在 input 內輸入任何文字，可以在 console 看到輸入的內容</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p2CdKxu.png\" alt=\"示意圖\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"實作避免使用者沒有輸入文字送出的警告文字\"><a href=\"#實作避免使用者沒有輸入文字送出的警告文字\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作避免使用者沒有輸入文字送出的警告文字\"></a>實作避免使用者沒有輸入文字送出的警告文字</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const checkRequired &#x3D; (inputArr&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  inputArr.forEach((input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;   trim() 為清除掉空格，使用者誤觸空格，可以避免掉存取資料\n    if(input.value.trim()&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;&#39;)&#123;\n      showError(input,&#39;is required&#39;)\n    &#125;else&#123;\n      showSuccess(input)\n    &#125;\n  &#125;))\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2UUAFnK.png\" alt=\"示意圖\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"實作將-is-required-警告文字-前方加上，是哪一個填空尚未填入\"><a href=\"#實作將-is-required-警告文字-前方加上，是哪一個填空尚未填入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作將 is required (警告文字)前方加上，是哪一個填空尚未填入\"></a>實作將 is required (警告文字)前方加上，是哪一個填空尚未填入</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const checkRequired &#x3D; (inputArr&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  inputArr.forEach((input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    if(input.value.trim() &#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;&#39; )&#123;\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 因為填空欄都已經綁上 html 標籤，直接取用 id 即可\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 使用 es6 語法&#96;$&#123;&#125; string&#96;，快速完成字串加上變數\n      showError(input,&#96;$&#123;input.id&#125; is required&#96;)\n    &#125;else&#123;\n      showSuccess(input)\n    &#125;\n  &#125;))\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lBYP7vK.png\" alt=\"示意圖\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"為了讓警示文字更正是，實作讓他字首為大寫\"><a href=\"#為了讓警示文字更正是，實作讓他字首為大寫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為了讓警示文字更正是，實作讓他字首為大寫\"></a>為了讓警示文字更正是，實作讓他字首為大寫</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; Check require\nconst checkRequired &#x3D; (inputArr&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  inputArr.forEach((input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    if(input.value.trim() &#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;&#39; )&#123;\n      showError(input,&#96;$&#123;getFiredName(input)&#125; is required&#96;)\n    &#125;else&#123;\n      showSuccess(input)\n    &#125;\n  &#125;))\n&#125;)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; Get fieldname\nconst getFiredName &#x3D; (input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 1. charAt() 語法意思為 取出原本字串的初始狀態，\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.charAt(0)&#x3D;&#39;B&#39; 大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.charAt(1)&#x3D;&#39;o&#39; 小寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.charAt(3)&#x3D;&#39;Y&#39; 大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 2. slice() 語法意思為拿掉第幾個值，回傳你一個&#39;新的陣列&#39;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;    slice(0,5) ## 含頭不含尾\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.slice(0)&#x3D;&#39;oY&#39; 大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.slice(2)&#x3D;&#39;Bo&#39; 大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F;     Ex: BoY.slice(0,2)&#x3D;&#39;Bo&#39; 大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 3. toUpperCase()轉為大寫\n&#x2F;&#x2F;    toLowerCase()轉為小寫\n\n&#x2F;* charAt(0)將 id 的首字拿出並 toUpperCase()轉為大寫，\n * 加上 slice(1) 去掉第一個字，並且回傳新的陣列物件*&#x2F;\n  return input.id.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+input.id.slice(1);\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Ci0l40.png\" alt=\"示意圖\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"實作檢查字數功能\"><a href=\"#實作檢查字數功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作檢查字數功能\"></a>實作檢查字數功能</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; Check input length\nconst checkLength &#x3D; ((input,min,max)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  if (input.value.length &lt; min ) &#123;\n    showError(input,&#96;$&#123;getFiredName(input)&#125; must be at least $&#123;min&#125;&#96;)\n  &#125;else if (input.value.length &gt; max) &#123;\n    showError(input,&#96;$&#123;getFiredName(input)&#125; must be less than $&#123;max&#125; characters&#96;)\n  &#125;else&#123;\n    showSuccess(input)\n  &#125;\n&#125;)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; Event Listener\nform.addEventListener(&#39;submit&#39;,(e)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  e.preventDefault();\n  checkRequired([username,email,password,confirmPassword])\n  checkLength(username,3,15)\n  checkLength(password,6,25)\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FlSoR3g.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"實作信箱確認，將原先的-isValidEmail-刪除\"><a href=\"#實作信箱確認，將原先的-isValidEmail-刪除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作信箱確認，將原先的 isValidEmail() 刪除\"></a>實作信箱確認，將原先的 isValidEmail() 刪除</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; Check Email is valid\nconst checkEmail &#x3D; (input&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  const re &#x3D; &#x2F;^(([^&lt;&gt;()[\\]\\\\.,;:\\s@&quot;]+(\\.[^&lt;&gt;()[\\]\\\\.,;:\\s@&quot;]+)*)|(&quot;.+&quot;))@((\\[[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\.[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\.[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\.[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\])|(([a-zA-Z\\-0-9]+\\.)+[a-zA-Z]&#123;2,&#125;))$&#x2F;;\n  if (re.test(input.value.trim())) &#123;\n    showSuccess(input)\n  &#125; else &#123;\n    showError(input, &#39;Email is not valid&#39;)\n  &#125;\n&#125;)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; Event Listener\nform.addEventListener(&#39;submit&#39;,(e)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  e.preventDefault();\n  checkRequired([username,email,password,confirmPassword])\n  checkLength(username,3,15)\n  checkLength(password,6,25)\n  checkEmail(email)\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"實作密碼跟再次輸入密碼欄位是否符合\"><a href=\"#實作密碼跟再次輸入密碼欄位是否符合\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作密碼跟再次輸入密碼欄位是否符合\"></a>實作密碼跟再次輸入密碼欄位是否符合</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; Check passwords match\nconst checkPasswordsMatch &#x3D; ((input1,input2)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  if (input1.value !&#x3D;&#x3D; input2.value) &#123;\n    showError(input2,&#39;Passwords do not match&#39;)\n  &#125;\n&#125;)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; Event Listener\nform.addEventListener(&#39;submit&#39;,(e)&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n  e.preventDefault();\n  checkRequired([username,email,password,confirmPassword])\n  checkLength(username,3,15)\n  checkLength(password,6,25)\n  checkEmail(email)\n  checkPasswordsMatch(password,confirmPassword)\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n\n","text":"延續上一份表單驗證筆記 重構是為了讓程式碼更加簡潔、可動性更高 先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的 if 判斷式if(email.value&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;&#39;)&#123; showError(email,&#39;Email is requi...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.8k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":43,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作品集","slug":"JavaScript/作品集","count":18,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript/作品集.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"作品集","slug":"作品集","count":19,"path":"api/tags/作品集.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%88%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E6%94%8F%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3%E7%9A%84-if-%E5%88%A4%E6%96%B7%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">先刪除這個攏長以及太多地方一樣的 if 判斷式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA-function-%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%99%A3%E5%88%97%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E8%91%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">更改為 function 將參數用陣列包裹著</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E9%80%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作避免使用者沒有輸入文字送出的警告文字</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E5%B0%87-is-required-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97-%E5%89%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%A1%AB%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作將 is required (警告文字)前方加上，是哪一個填空尚未填入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%93%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%9B%B4%E6%AD%A3%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E5%AD%97%E9%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">為了讓警示文字更正是，實作讓他字首為大寫</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E5%AD%97%E6%95%B8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作檢查字數功能</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E4%BF%A1%E7%AE%B1%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%8E%9F%E5%85%88%E7%9A%84-isValidEmail-%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作信箱確認，將原先的 isValidEmail() 刪除</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E8%B7%9F%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E6%AC%84%E4%BD%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作密碼跟再次輸入密碼欄位是否符合</span></a>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"初次實作表單驗證","uid":"669e060f0bbf70a859b2f8a42af00cd3","slug":"表單驗證","date":"2021-01-28T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.562Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/表單驗證.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":" 長度限制： html : &lt;input&gt;maxlength=&#39;10&#39;&lt;input/&gt; 版型限制 (email) :&lt;input type = &#39;email&#39; 資料驗證結果之欄位樣式設定當資料驗證結果可於偽類選擇器中設...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":568,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":2,"path":"api/categories/HTML.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":2,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"(Project) 表單驗證實作","uid":"e9c5ecd175c22fa84b430eb677ccf7bf","slug":"表單驗證實作","date":"2021-01-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.506Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/表單驗證實作.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"DemoHTML首先 html 先建立 container 來包裹表單&lt;div class&#x3D;&#39;container&#39;&gt; &lt;form&gt; &lt;&#x2F;form&gt; &lt;&#x2F;div&gt; 建立表單標籤,加上 id...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"8k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":43,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作品集","slug":"JavaScript/作品集","count":18,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript/作品集.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"作品集","slug":"作品集","count":19,"path":"api/tags/作品集.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}